title: Independent candidate Rangeez Ahmed wins PK-49 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Rangeez Ahmed has won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK-49 Swabi-1 by securing 36,692 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was JUI-P’s Ghafoor Khan Jadoon who bagged 15,312 votes.
Voters’ turn-out remained 38.56 per cent.
